<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA33">
<l>nūlaṟivu pēci nuḻaivilā tārtirika</l>
<l>nīla maṇimiṭaṟṟā ṉīrmaiyē - mēlulanta</l>
<l>tekkōlat tevvuruvā yettavaṅkaḷ ceyvārkku</l>
<l>makkōlat tavvuruvē yām</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Speaking of the knowledge from treatises let those without subtelty roam about.</l>
<l>Surpassing is the nature of him with a blue saphire throat.</l>
<l>For those who do whatever penance as to whatever beauty, to whatever form,</l>
<l>that beauty, that form will be [his].</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
